</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/4768/xautolock-frustration/?comment=4778#comment-4778</link><description>See if double-quoting the commands helps. If not, maybe placing it in one of your start-up scripts (such as ~/.xinitrc) would work.</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Oct 2014 16:50:27 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/4768/xautolock-frustration/?comment=4778#comment-4778</guid></item></channel></rss>